 candidate. Include previous work experience, education or achievements that would be beneficial. And list any preferred hard and soft skills. Example Caterer requirements High School Diploma or GED Food handler permit Knowledge of food safety standards Previous experience in food service setting is preferred Excellent customer service skills and attention to detail Positive, proactive attitude and a team player Caterer related job titles: Catering Worker Lead Caterer Banquet Server Food Service Attendant Food Services Aide Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
